premise_source_doc_sentence: The species made its debut in the film Alien  (  1979  )  , and reappeared in the sequels Aliens  (  1986  )  , Alien 3  (  1992  )  , and Alien : Resurrection  (  1997  )  , as well as the crossover franchise Alien vs. Predator  (  2004  )  and Aliens vs. Predator : Requiem  (  2007  )  .

, a crossover with the Predator franchise produced the Alien vs. Predator series , which includes Alien vs. Predator  (  2004  )  and Aliens vs. Predator : Requiem  (  2007  )  , and also a prequel series of films , which includes Prometheus  (  2012  )  and Alien : Covenant  (  2017  )  .

It also launched Weaver 's acting career by providing her with her first lead role , and the story of her character Ellen Ripley 's encounters with the Alien creatures became the thematic thread that ran through the sequels Aliens  (  1986  )  , Alien 3  (  1992  )  and Alien : Resurrection  (  1997  )  .
The `` Alien ''  (  also referred to as `` Xenomorph '' or `` Xenomorph XX121 ''  )  is a fictional endoparasitoid extraterrestrial species that is the eponymous antagonist of the Alien film series .
Alien launched the Alien franchise and is chronologically the first of the main series , with the prequel series set in an earlier timeframe .
